<plot>This Universal musical short features Latin American rhythms played by Carlos Molina and His Orchestra. The orchestra, complete with maraca's, plays "Rhumbatella", "Bim Bam Bum" and "You Never Say Yes," and a number of other musical numbers from south of the border. Armida and Bobby Rivers add their dancing and singing talents.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?120637</url></doc>
